      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PEAKY AVENGER (8) drawn the outside box and could get a clear run. Was below best last time when 7th and beaten 7 lengths at this track (23.02). Form here at this distance is strong including two wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Looks the one to beat on her best form. FLAMING FOX (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (23.47) at this track latest. Has a good record at this journey. Should be in this for a long way. CRACKERJACK HOPS (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (23.56) last time in a Mix 3/4 at Horsham. Solid winning record at this trip. Leading chance. MISS JAZZ (4) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - solid claims again.",
